Oworonshoki bụ ógbè dị na Lagos State, Nigeria

Obodo a nọ n'okpuru Kosofe Local Government Area nke Steeti Lagos. N'ihe gbasara ala, Oworonshoki bụ ihe dị mkpa na steeti Lagos ka ọ na-ejikọ mpaghara Mainland na Island nke Lagos site na Third Mainland Bridge
Ọ na-enwekwa ọdụ ụgbọ okporo ígwè Apapa Oworonshoki Expressway.
N'okpuru Kosofe Local Government Area, Oworonshoki nwere ngalaba abụọ, Ward A na Ward B.
Okporo ụzọ kachasị ogologo na Oworonshoki bụ okporo ụzọ Oworo.
